ts binaries to /usr/X11R6/bin may be outside your PATH, and\n   you will need to update the configuration on your system accordingly.\n\n   The Debian metapackages used to install all of the X Window System have\n   been changed with X11R7. They used to be named x-window-system and\n   x-window-system-core. Now there is only one metapackage named \"xorg\". It\n   is highly recommended that you install this metapackage in order to get\n   a fully working installation of the X Window System.\n\n -- David Nusinow <dnusinow@debian.org>  Thu, 13 Apr 2006 22:13:17 -0400','2015-12-08 00:00:00','34aab40c713182b3d30d717c83bb6455','',1,0),(2994,'x11proto-input-dev',NULL,'','',0,6,'flooringdepot','x11proto-input (2.3.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium\n\n  * New upstream release.\n  * Remove Cyril from Uploaders.\n\n -- Julien Cristau <jcristau@debian.org>  Sun, 13 Jul 2014 10:17:18 +0200\n\nx11proto-input (2.3-1) unstable; urgency=low\n\n  [ Maarten Lankhorst ]\n  * New upstream release.\n\n -- Julien Cristau <jcristau@debian.org>  Sun, 09 Jun 2013 14:51:56 +0200\n\nx11proto-input (2.2-1) unstable; urgency=low\n\n  * New upstream release.\n  * Upload to unstable\n\n -- Julien Cristau <jcristau@debian.org>  Sun, 15 Apr 2012 16:17:02 +0200\n\nx11proto-input (2.1.99.6-1) experimental; urgency=low\n\n  [ Chase Douglas ]\n  * New upstream release candidate.\n\n -- Cyril Brulebois <kibi@debian.org>  Fri, 10 Feb 2012 21:53:18 +0100\n\nx11proto-input (2.1.99.5-2) experimental; urgency=low','2015-12-08 00:00:00','1dd1b96c0b0b1286ef8cf4f27117edf8','',1,0),(2996,'xauth',NULL,'','',0,6,'flooringdepot','xauth (1:1.0.9-1) unstable; urgency=medium\n\n  * New upstream release.\n  * Remove Cyril from Uploaders.\n  * Disable silent build rules and silent tests.\n  * Add build-dep on cmdtest for make check.\n\n -- Julien Cristau <jcristau@debian.org>  Sun, 13 Jul 2014 10:34:06 +0200\n\nxauth (1:1.0.7-1) unstable; urgency=low\n\n  * New upstream release.\n\n -- Julien Cristau <jcristau@debian.org>  T